# Component & Page Rules

## Page Structure Pattern
Every page must follow this skeleton:
```tsx
import type { Metadata } from 'next'
import { Navbar } from '@/components/Navbar'
import { Footer } from '@/components/Footer'
import { ScrollReveal } from '@/components/ScrollReveal'

export const metadata: Metadata = {
  title: 'Page Title',
  description: '...',
}

export default function PageName() {
  return (
    <>
      <Navbar />
      <main>
        {/* Page Header — dark navy bg */}
        <section className="bg-navy-950 pt-36 pb-20 relative overflow-hidden">
          <div className="absolute inset-0 bg-grid-pattern bg-grid opacity-30" />
          <div className="container-custom relative z-10">
            <ScrollReveal>
              <div className="label-tag-light mb-4">Section Label</div>
              <h1 className="font-display font-extrabold text-display text-white mb-6">
                Page Headline
              </h1>
              <p className="font-body text-white/60 text-lg max-w-2xl leading-relaxed">
                Subheadline text.
              </p>
            </ScrollReveal>
          </div>
        </section>

        {/* Content sections */}
      </main>
      <Footer />
    </>
  )
}
```

## Section Alternation Pattern
Alternate section backgrounds for visual rhythm:
```
Section 1: bg-white
Section 2: bg-neutral-50
Section 3: bg-navy-900 (dark accent)
Section 4: bg-blue-brand (primary CTA)
```

## Section Internal Structure
```tsx
<section className="section-pad bg-white">
  <div className="container-custom">
    {/* Label + Heading */}
    <ScrollReveal className="mb-16">
      <div className="label-tag mb-3">Section Label</div>
      <h2 className="font-display font-bold text-display text-navy-900">
        Heading
      </h2>
    </ScrollReveal>

    {/* Content */}
    <StaggerReveal className="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
      {items.map(item => <Card key={item.id} {...item} />)}
    </StaggerReveal>
  </div>
</section>
```

## Typography Hierarchy (inside page body)
```tsx
// Section label
<div className="label-tag mb-3">Kata Kunci Singkat</div>

// Main heading
<h2 className="font-display font-bold text-display text-navy-900">
  Judul Section
</h2>

// Sub heading
<h3 className="font-display font-semibold text-headline text-navy-900">
  Sub Judul
</h3>

// Body text
<p className="font-body text-neutral-500 leading-relaxed">
  Paragraf konten.
</p>

// Mono label / metadata
<span className="font-mono text-[11px] text-neutral-400 uppercase tracking-widest">
  Tahun / Kategori / Status
</span>
```

## Cards
```tsx
// Standard service card (light bg)
<div className="service-card">
  <div className="text-3xl mb-4">{icon}</div>
  <h3 className="font-display font-bold text-navy-900 text-lg mb-2">{title}</h3>
  <p className="font-body text-neutral-500 text-sm leading-relaxed">{desc}</p>
  <div className="mt-6 w-8 h-0.5 bg-blue-brand group-hover:w-16 transition-all duration-300" />
</div>

// Dark card (navy bg)
<div className="bg-navy-900 p-8 relative">
  <div className="absolute top-0 left-0 right-0 h-0.5 bg-blue-brand" />
  {/* content */}
</div>
```

## CTA Sections (end of page)
Always end pages with a CTA section:
```tsx
<section className="section-pad bg-blue-brand relative overflow-hidden">
  <div className="absolute inset-0 bg-grid-pattern bg-grid opacity-20" />
  <div className="container-custom relative z-10 text-center">
    <ScrollReveal>
      <div className="label-tag-light mb-4">Action Label</div>
      <h2 className="font-display font-extrabold text-display text-white mb-6">
        CTA Heading
      </h2>
      <p className="font-body text-white/70 text-lg mb-10 max-w-xl mx-auto">
        Supporting text.
      </p>
      <div className="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-4">
        <a href="https://wa.me/6281219445330" className="btn-whatsapp">WhatsApp</a>
        <Link href="/kontak" className="btn-outline">Form Kontak</Link>
      </div>
    </ScrollReveal>
  </div>
</section>
```

## WhatsApp Links
Always use this format with pre-filled message:
```tsx
<a
  href="https://wa.me/6281219445330?text=ENCODED_MESSAGE"
  target="_blank"
  rel="noopener noreferrer"
>
```

## Image Handling
- Use `next/image` for all images in `/public`
- Always provide `alt` text in Indonesian
- Use `fill` + `object-cover` for card/section images
- Use explicit `width` and `height` for inline images
